==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chela
<hw>Che"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind.
<ets>ch⟦emac⟧la</ets>, orig., slave, fr. Skr.
